title: Best Case/Worst Case: Lakers, Nets, Bucks, and Suns I The Answer
description:
Rob Mahoney fills in for Chris, joining Seerat to run through some of the best- and worst-case scenarios for four of the NBA’s projected top teams, the Lakers, Nets (14:46), Bucks, and Suns (42:14).
Hosts: Seerat Sohi, Rob Mahoney
Producer: Troy Farkas
